  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Research Collaboration Workshops</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A series of workshops bringing together past and current Newton Fund award holders of ODA-eligible projects to develop further ODA-eligible interdisciplinary and cross-border research collaborations drawing on their Newton Fund awards</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We will be delivering of a number of research collaboration workshops and networking/dissemination events in Brazil and South Africa. These events are expected to generate significant impact by solidifying links with partner organisations overseas, by further building the knowledge and skills of the award holders and by facilitating ideas and connections that are likely to extend beyond the Newton Fund&#x2019;s lifespan.</narrative>
  </description>
